Verslag van de nieuwe Avengers Doomsday X-Men en Scarlet Witch. Elizabeth Olsen keert terug, wat er met Scarlet Witch is gebeurd. Avengers Doomsday NYCC Teaser en Comic Con Panel. Comic Book Accurate X-Men, Robert Downey Jr Doctor Doom. Fantastic Four ontmoet The Avengers, Avengers Doomsday Trailer D23 Leak Breakdown en Easter Eggs. Nieuwe personages, Doctor Dooms Masterplan, Deadpool, Spider-Man. Problemen tijdens de opnames van Avengers Doomsday. Ryan Reynolds volgende Deadpool-project, X-Force-films, Avengers Doomsday, Secret Wars-plannen. Aankondiging Deadpool 4. Ryan Reynolds legt de toekomst van Deadpool-films en -tv-series bij Marvel uit. Avengers 6 Secret Wars X-Men-plan uitgelegd. Marvel Phase 7 Mutant Saga, nieuwe X-Men films.

Waarom Ryan Reynolds werd aangeklaagd voor Deadpool en Wolverine. Marvel-grappen, verwijderde sc√®nes, rechtszaak Ryan Reynolds en Blake Lively. Wat er gaat gebeuren. En waarom Ryan Reynolds zich geen zorgen hoeft te maken. En hoe Marvel, Deadpool en Wolverine onderdeel werden van de rechtszaak.

X-23, Wolverine vs Hulk, verwijderde sc√®nes in Gambit, verwijderde sc√®nes in Blade, Sabretooth, Wolverine vs Sabretooth. Deadpool vs Disney-grappen, Kevin Feige Marvel-grappen en het doorbreken van de Vierde Muur. Deadpool en Wolverine-grappen na de aftiteling. Sc√®ne met Evil Iron Man, cameosc√®ne in The Punisher, X-Men-sc√®nes, meer Deadpool-varianten, meer Wolverine-varianten. Adamantium uitgelegd. Ben Affleck Daredevil-referenties, Elektra, waarom Deadpool Wolverine redt, de X-Men, Fantastic Four en Deadpool redt de MCU. Hoe Deadpool en Wolverine Avengers 6 Secret Wars voorbereiden met Battleworld en Loki Seizoen 2 eindigt met God Loki Crossover Easter Eggs.

Waarom Marvel de MCU reboot, alle Marvel-films en Disney Plus Marvel-tv-series met Avengers 6 Secret Wars. En wat gaat er veranderen met al de Avengers, New Iron Man, X-Men Mutants zoals Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man en andere personages die Marvel eerder niet kon gebruiken zoals ze wilden in eerdere films?

Alla scoperta dei nuovi Avengers: Doomsday, X-Men e Scarlet Witch. Il ritorno di Elizabeth Olsen, cosa √® successo a Scarlet Witch. Teaser di Avengers: Doomsday al NYCC e panel del Comic-Con. X-Men accurati come nei fumetti, Dottor Destino di Robert Downey Jr. I Fantastici Quattro incontrano gli Avengers, analisi delle fughe di notizie del trailer di Avengers: Doomsday al D23 e Easter Egg. Nuovi personaggi, il piano generale del Dottor Destino, Deadpool, Spider-Man. Problemi sul set di Avengers: Doomsday. Il prossimo progetto di Ryan Reynolds su Deadpool, film sulla X-Force, Avengers: Doomsday, piani per Secret Wars. Annuncio di Deadpool 4. Ryan Reynolds spiega il futuro dei film e delle serie TV di Deadpool alla Marvel. Spiegazione del piano per gli X-Men di Avengers: Secret Wars 6. Saga dei Mutanti Marvel Fase 7, Nuovi Film sugli X-Men.

Perch√© Ryan Reynolds √® stato citato in giudizio per Deadpool e Wolverine. Battute Marvel, Scene Eliminate, Causa contro Ryan Reynolds e Blake Lively. Cosa succeder√† di conseguenza. E perch√© Ryan Reynolds non deve preoccuparsi. E come la Marvel, Deadpool e Wolverine siano stati coinvolti nella causa.

X-23, Wolverine contro Hulk, Scene Eliminate di Gambit, Scene Eliminate di Blade, Sabretooth, Wolverine contro Sabretooth. Battute su Deadpool contro Disney, Battute su Kevin Feige Marvel e Rottura della Quarta Parete. Battute sulla Scena Post-Crediti di Deadpool e Wolverine. Scena con Iron Man Cattivo, Scena con il Cameo di The Punisher, Scene sugli X-Men, Altre Varianti di Deadpool, Altre Varianti di Wolverine. Spiegazione dell'Adamantio. Riferimenti a Ben Affleck su Daredevil, Elektra, Perch√© Deadpool salva Wolverine, Gli X-Men, I Fantastici Quattro e Deadpool salvano l'MCU. Come Deadpool e Wolverine preparano il terreno per Avengers 6 Secret Wars con Battleworld e Loki, che si concluder√† con Easter Egg del crossover con Dio Loki.

Perch√© la Marvel sta riavviando l'MCU, tutti i film Marvel e le serie TV Disney+ Marvel con Avengers 6 Secret Wars. E cosa cambier√† con tutti gli Avengers, il Nuovo Iron Man, i Mutanti degli X-Men come Wolverine, Deadpool, i Fantastici Quattro, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man e altri personaggi che la Marvel non era riuscita a usare come voleva nei film precedenti?

nl-NL.title: Halo: Campaign Evolved | The Silent Cartographer ‚Äì 13 minuten gameplay-demo
nl-NL.description:
Een volledige playthrough van de Halo: Campaign Evolved work-in-progress De Silent Cartographer-demo van het Halo World Championship 2025, vastgelegd vanuit een pre-release build op Xbox Series X.

Halo: Campaign Evolved, dat in 2026 naar Xbox Series X|S, pc en PlayStation 5 komt, is een getrouwe maar gemoderniseerde remake van de campagne van Halo: Combat Evolved, helemaal opnieuw opgebouwd met high-definition graphics, verfijnde besturing, splitscreen co-op voor 2 spelers op de console, online co-op voor maximaal 4 spelers op de console en pc, 3 nieuwe missies, een uitgebreid arsenaal aan wapens, voertuigen, nieuwe vijanden en meer.

Nu op de verlanglijst zetten!

en.description:
A full playthrough of the Halo: Campaign Evolved work-in-progress The Silent Cartographer demo from the Halo World Championship 2025, captured from a pre-release build on Xbox Series X. 

Halo: Campaign Evolved, coming to Xbox Series X|S, PC, and PlayStation 5 in 2026, is a faithful yet modernized remake of Halo: Combat Evolved‚Äôs campaign, rebuilt from the ground up with high-definition visuals, refined controls, 2-player splitscreen co-op on console, up to 4-player online co-op on console and PC, 3 new missions, an expanded arsenal of weapons, vehicles, new enemies, and more.

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Release Trailer (Telugu) | Prabhas, Rana | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad 
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov
Dance Choreographers: Prem Rakshit, Shankar, Dinesh Kumar, Jani
Editor: Tammiraju 
Costume Designer: Rama Rajamouli, Prashanti Tripirneni 
Dialogues:
Telugu - C.H. Vijay Kumar, Ajay Kumar G
Hindi - Manoj Muntashir
Tamil - Karky

snippet.title: Tee Grizzley - Voicemail (feat. Rod Wave) [Official Video]
snippet.description:
The official video for Tee Grizzley's "Voicemail" featuring @RodWaveOfficial, out now!
Shot by @JerryPHD üé•

Stream "Voicemail": https://teegrizzley.lnk.to/voicemail

Subscribe to Tee Grizzley's Channel: http://flyt.it/SubscribeTee

Follow Tee:
https://www.tiktok.com/@tee_grizzley
https://www.instagram.com/teegrizzley/
https://twitter.com/teegrizzley
https://www.facebook.com/teegrizzley1/
https://open.spotify.com/artist/6AUl0ykLLpvTktob97x9hO?si=xNQXzi90TwSK8oYD4s5JsA
https://music.apple.com/us/artist/tee-grizzley/1177271472

#TeeGrizzley #GrizzleyGang #RodWave #Voicemail

‚Ñó 2025 Grizzley Gang Music under exclusive distribution by 300 Entertainment

LYRICS

[Intro: Rod Wave]
Mm, yeah, yeah
I was tellin' that bitch, Tee Grizzley, bitch, you gotta come to my world
You know what I'm sayin'? This that real shit
Mm, the city, woah, woah, woah
Yeah, yeah
Look, look, uh

[Verse 1: Rod Wave]
Crazy feelin' in my heart, too much on my brain
I be poppin' Perkies back to back, now I can't feel a thing
No matter what I'm feelin', I'm gon' keep it to myself
I be dreamin' 'bout unc, been seein' death since you left and
Court dates and funerals
Mama, this your baby, never stop prayin'
Soon as I go to sleep, my phone start ringin'
Soon as I find some peace, here come the blog pages
On the phone with my mama, ma, I was 'sleep when you called
I clicked over for smacker, no, I pressed one for my dog
Talked to my daughter on FaceTime, it's healin' my heart
Sometimes it get to killin' me, hope this ain't how she 'member me
Bae, I'm thug to the bone, I ain't lookin' for sympathy
I been thuggin' so long, in the street, in the industry
You know you can hit my phone if you need me
But who can I call with my back against the wall? (Ayy, ayy)

[Chorus: Rod Wave & Tee Grizzley]
My daughter askin', "Where you at? When you comin' back?"
My girl askin' me, "What's wrong? You need to relax"
So many people on my phone talkin' this and that, uh
Now, what's wrong? Leave me alone
Can't get no sleep, bitches abusin' my number
Either the tattlers got questions or bitches askin' for money
A thousand problems every time my phone ring
I let it ring, I don't know what to say (Yeah, yeah)
Uh, I don't know what to say (Yeah, yeah)
I don't know what to say (I don't even know what the fuck you sayin')
(Know what to say) Yeah, yeah (What to say)

[Post-Chorus: Tee Grizzley]
That shit ain't gon' mean nothin'
Ain't nothin' enough, it feel like
Nothin' you say even matter type shit, they can't even hear that shit, ah
[Verse 2: Tee Grizzley & Rod Wave]
I get to a check and bounce (Fuck on), niggas out here checkin' out (Niggas
out here dyin')
I was out here homeless walkin', now my wrist a car, neck a house (No cap)
Slave master how I whip the 'Bach, walk around with a million cash
I ain't posted, though, I was low with it, everything ain't for the internet (You
know?)
Miss my pops, God, please, can You just think about givin' him back?
Brodie, once that money gone, it's gone, you better remember to stack
Plugged the power to the neighbor house, we was late on bills, I remember
that
You don't get shit just for bein' real, you supposed to be, they be forgettin' that
(Fuck)
Hit the club, I ain't buy no bottles, but I hit the hood and got granny crib
remodeled (I did)
G-lock full of hollows 'cause lettin' 'em get me too big of a pill to swallow (Can't
let 'em)
Wanted to box, looked up and cases was all I had to fight (Damn)
Wanted to go to the league, I ain't make it, but I still turned out alright (I'm
cool)
Fought in school and had to fight in jail, maybe I'm the problem (Maybe it's
me)
Niggas got money in my face and left me broke, I should've robbed 'em
(Should've got they ass)
Seen my nigga was 'bout to crash out, feel like I could've stopped him (Damn)
It ain't 'bout gettin' to the top (What it's 'bout?), it's 'bout gettin' from off of the
bottom, nigga (Ayy, ayy)

[Chorus: Rod Wave & Tee Grizzley]
My daughter askin', "Where you at? When you comin' back?"
My girl askin' me, "What's wrong? You need to relax" (Yeah)
So many people on my phone, talkin' this and that, uh (What?)
Now, what's wrong? Leave me alone (Fuck on)
Can't get no sleep, bitches abusin' my number
Either the tattlers got questions or bitches askin' for money
A thousand problems every time my phone ring
I let it ring (Let me call you right back), I don't know what to say (I don't even
know what motherfuckers be wantin' to feel like, yeah, yeah)
Uh, I don't know what to say (What the fuck to say to these people, gang, like,
yeah, yeah)
I don't know what to say
(Know what to say) Yeah, yeah (What to say)
[Outro: Tee Grizzley]
Just let me go a couple days just without hearin' from nobody
You feel me? You know I'll call everybody in a couple days, man
This shit too much right now

snippet.title: Love is Blind Season 9: The Reunion | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
If this season of Love is Blind left you blindsided, just wait until the reunion. It's time to set the stories straight and reveal the biggest shockers of all. Watch together when Love is Blind: The Reunion premieres on Wednesday, October 29th at 9PM ET/6PM PT, only on Netflix.

The Love is Blind S9 pod squad will join hosts Nick and Vanessa Lachey to reveal where their relationships stand today and revisit the moments that made us all wonder: is love truly blind?

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81720506

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Love is Blind Season 9: The Reunion | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Big reveals come to light as this season's Pod Squad answer burning questions about their love lives and shoot their shot at getting closure.

snippet.title: Sailing - Old School RuneScape‚Äôs NEW SKILL | Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Sailing, Old School RuneScape's first EVER new skill, is coming on November 19th! Master your skills at sea, upgrade your boat, explore and discover new islands packed with brand-new resources, rewards, training methods, bosses and more. We've worked on this skill in close collaboration with our community, giving players the opportunity to vote on key milestones and shape it's direction from the start, and on November 19th, the ocean will open and come to life.

Set Sail on November 19th yer wee landblubbers and play OSRS' 24th skill.
This trailer was made in collaboration with community artist Uber: https://uber-osrs.carrd.co/

Old School RuneScape is a retro game version of RuneScape from 2007 which we returned at the community's request. The community controls the developmental direction of Old School RuneScape by voting on which updates it would like to receive.

The world's largest and most popular MMORPG, Old School RuneScape has been played by over 260 million players since the 2001 release of RuneScape. Old School RuneScape unites the intricate mechanics of modern MMOs with the nostalgic point-and-click gameplay of early role-playing games.

Old School RuneScape is free to download and play, however, the game also offers players the opportunity to purchase in-game items. Please see the PEGI information page for more information: https://pegi.info/search-pegi?q=runescape

nl-NL.title: Zeilen - De NIEUWE VAARDIGHEID van Old School RuneScape | Offici√´le releasedatumtrailer
nl-NL.description:
Zeilen, de allereerste nieuwe vaardigheid van Old School RuneScape, komt op 19 november! Verbeter je vaardigheden op zee, upgrade je boot, verken en ontdek nieuwe eilanden vol gloednieuwe grondstoffen, beloningen, trainingsmethoden, bazen en meer. We hebben aan deze vaardigheid gewerkt in nauwe samenwerking met onze community, waardoor spelers vanaf het begin de mogelijkheid hebben om te stemmen op belangrijke mijlpalen en de richting ervan te bepalen. Op 19 november opent de oceaan zich en komt tot leven.

Zet op 19 november de zeilen, jullie kleine landblubbers, en speel de 24e vaardigheid van OSRS.
Deze trailer is gemaakt in samenwerking met community artist Uber: https://uber-osrs.carrd.co/

Old School RuneScape is een retroversie van RuneScape uit 2007 die we op verzoek van de community hebben teruggebracht. De community bepaalt de ontwikkelingsrichting van Old School RuneScape door te stemmen op welke updates ze willen ontvangen.

's Werelds grootste en populairste MMORPG, Old School RuneScape, is sinds de release van RuneScape in 2001 door meer dan 260 miljoen spelers gespeeld. Old School RuneScape combineert de complexe mechanica van moderne MMO's met de nostalgische point-and-click-gameplay van vroege rollenspellen.

Old School RuneScape is gratis te downloaden en te spelen, maar de game biedt spelers ook de mogelijkheid om in-game items te kopen. Raadpleeg de PEGI-informatiepagina voor meer informatie: https://pegi.info/search-pegi?q=runescape

id.title: Berlayar - KETERAMPILAN BARU RuneScape Jadul | Trailer Tanggal Rilis Resmi
id.description:
Berlayar, skill baru pertama di Old School RuneScape, akan hadir pada 19 November! Kuasai skill Anda di laut, tingkatkan kapal Anda, jelajahi dan temukan pulau-pulau baru yang penuh dengan sumber daya, hadiah, metode pelatihan, bos, dan banyak lagi yang baru. Kami telah mengembangkan skill ini bekerja sama erat dengan komunitas kami, memberikan pemain kesempatan untuk memilih tonggak penting dan membentuk arahnya sejak awal, dan pada 19 November, lautan akan terbuka dan hidup kembali.

Berlayarlah pada 19 November, para landblubber kecil, dan mainkan skill ke-24 OSRS.
Trailer ini dibuat bekerja sama dengan seniman komunitas Uber: https://uber-osrs.carrd.co/

Old School RuneScape adalah versi game retro RuneScape dari tahun 2007 yang kami kembalikan atas permintaan komunitas. Komunitas mengontrol arah pengembangan Old School RuneScape dengan memilih pembaruan yang ingin mereka terima.

MMORPG terbesar dan terpopuler di dunia, Old School RuneScape, telah dimainkan oleh lebih dari 260 juta pemain sejak RuneScape dirilis pada tahun 2001. Old School RuneScape memadukan mekanika rumit MMO modern dengan gameplay point-and-click yang nostalgia dari game role-playing terdahulu.

Old School RuneScape gratis untuk diunduh dan dimainkan, namun game ini juga menawarkan kesempatan bagi pemain untuk membeli item dalam game. Silakan lihat halaman informasi PEGI untuk informasi selengkapnya: https://pegi.info/search-pegi?q=runescape

en.title: Sailing - Old School RuneScape‚Äôs NEW SKILL | Official Release Date Trailer
en.description:
Sailing, Old School RuneScape's first EVER new skill, is coming on November 19th! Master your skills at sea, upgrade your boat, explore and discover new islands packed with brand-new resources, rewards, training methods, bosses and more. We've worked on this skill in close collaboration with our community, giving players the opportunity to vote on key milestones and shape it's direction from the start, and on November 19th, the ocean will open and come to life.

Set Sail on November 19th yer wee landblubbers and play OSRS' 24th skill.
This trailer was made in collaboration with community artist Uber: https://uber-osrs.carrd.co/

Old School RuneScape is a retro game version of RuneScape from 2007 which we returned at the community's request. The community controls the developmental direction of Old School RuneScape by voting on which updates it would like to receive.

The world's largest and most popular MMORPG, Old School RuneScape has been played by over 260 million players since the 2001 release of RuneScape. Old School RuneScape unites the intricate mechanics of modern MMOs with the nostalgic point-and-click gameplay of early role-playing games.

Old School RuneScape is free to download and play, however, the game also offers players the opportunity to purchase in-game items. Please see the PEGI information page for more information: https://pegi.info/search-pegi?q=runescape

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Searching For A World That Doesn‚Äôt Exist
snippet.description:
"At the crossroads, don't turn left" is the first line of a book that Avery did not write. A strange mine suddenly appears in Avery's world with an odd book in a chest, but as he explores further, Avery finds a tunnel leading to a Minecraft world that shouldn't exist. And he isn't the only thing in this world either...

Avery's Channel:  @averylargemayo 


DISCLAIMER!! Don't read for spoilers: ----


The ARG in this video is one that I created specifically for this video. Upcoming videos will continue to feature ARGs I find in the wild, but I wanted to experiment with storytelling and see if I can make an entertaining mystery watch myself.

Some fun tidbits about this video - it was made over the course of 4 months and I have some thoughts but I think the second half of the video is both very experimental and very fun to watch. Multiple minutes of no voice over and just music?? Never done that before, hopefully this doesn't age badly. The CIPHER though goodness gracious. The cipher room d3rLord runs into was meant to be almost unsolvable with cipher stacking. But I made the cardinal sin of stacking two substitution ciphers so it can be solved with literally just a basic vigenere. The whole point was to ego boost d3rLord but now he's just yapping about solving a basic shift cipher. Oh well... I also think the whispers in the tunnel might be the worst flaw of this video. I liked the idea in theory but sounds a tad corny. The rest of the vid I really like though. I hope you enjoy! 



‚û§‚û§ Twitter: https://twitter.com/WifiesWasTaken
‚û§‚û§ Discord: https://discord.gg/zAWUuWb


‚û§‚û§Links: MUSIC USED/LICENSED:

EPIDEMIC SOUND MUSIC I USE: https://share.epidemicsound.com/1xis5q/?playlist=uad3vzakh605efvoqoi24llhnpr9lm2y

LEMMiNO - Encounters
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfEG3swhViQ
CC BY-SA 4.0


This is NOT a series called Minecraft VVSauce where I explore random features of Minecraft. Not Secret Minecraft things or Minecraft lore (like Game Theory) or Escape Rooms, but a spooky ARG!! But not really args, this is unfiction. A tangential but not identical genre. It's basically a cool mystery story. See you next time.

Lyrics:

When you can‚Äôt win
For losing
And the beggars start choosing the chaos in your head

Calls the cracks to start showing
All knowing all glowing with the light of the
Dying to raise the dead, oh

You‚Äôre a world away
But you‚Äôre still the same
I know you by your heart
And I will call you by your name

It‚Äôs a long way
From the crack to the break

You know that I remember everything

Steady yourself
And your tumbleweed words

Be a street corner preacher
Or just feed the birds

But don‚Äôt hold to yourself
With hard mortar and stone

Be a rubber band man
Make the water your bones

Dying just to live
Now

You‚Äôre a world away
But you‚Äôre still the same

I know you by your heart
And I will call you by your name

And it‚Äôs a long way
From the crack to the break

You know that I remember everything

When I said forever

You said get back in the car
Nothing lasts forever babe
You know it breaks my heart

And I‚Äôll call you anything that you like

And I am free and I‚Äôm able
To call you the second that you die
Just to live
Now

You‚Äôre a world away
But you‚Äôre still the same

I know you by your heart
And I will call you by your name

And it‚Äôs a long way
From the crack to the break

You know that I remember everything

When I said forever
You said get back in the car
Nothing lasts forever babe
You know it breaks my heart

You‚Äôre a world away
But you‚Äôre still the same

You know that I remember everything

New ink on your skin
Red lips in the dark

Nothing lasts forever babe
You know it breaks my heart

Put a shiver on your skin
Do your hair in the car

If nothing lasts forever babe
Then can we make a start?

snippet.title: One Last Time - Ariana Grande (Acoustic cover by Emily Linge)
snippet.description:
‚ÄúOne Last Time‚Äù by Ariana Grande - Acoustic cover by Emily Linge. 
Subscribe: https://youtube.com/@EmilyLinge/?sub_confirmation=1 | Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/1oHuewfSrJgCviOzYBcr5A 
Watch the newest videos: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLG9gKlFD44lR-LpqMMcg8EmOQObae_iCA&playnext=1&index=2

Special thanks to @OvidioDeFerrari for helping with the piano arrangement.
Thanks also to Mix and Master Elvis Garagic, MORE Studios Dubai, UAE 

Lyrics:

I was a liar
I gave in to the fire
I know I should've fought it
At least I'm being honest
Feel like a failure
'Cause I know that I failed you
I should've done you better
'Cause you don't want a liar

And I know, and I know, and I know
She gives you everything
But, boy, I couldn't give it to you
And I know, and I know, and I know
That you got everything
But I got nothing here without you

So one last time
I need to be the one who takes you home
One more time
I promise, after that, I'll let you go
Baby, I don't care if you got her in your heart
All I really care is you wake up in my arms
One last time
I need to be the one who takes you home

I don't deserve it
I know I don't deserve it

GRAMMY¬Æ Award-nominated songwriter, vocalist, multi-instrumentalist, and producer Wolfgang Van Halen continues to separate Mammoth from the pack. The music stands alone on a foundation anchored by his impressive sonic proficiency (across drums, bass, keys, and guitar) and airtight arena-size hooks with unforgettable vocals. He harbors an irresistible signature sound, inventive vision, and incomparable identity vaunted by a fervent global fanbase. For as unique as the music is, his story so far proves to be just as unprecedented. This is arguably the first hard rock act to genuinely break out from ground zero in the 2020‚Äôs, generating north of 100 million streams, toppling charts, and selling out headline tours less than five years since its debut. Back in 2021, Mammoth‚Äôs first offering, Mammoth WVH, took flight, bowing at #12 on the Billboard 200 and capturing #1 on three Billboard charts‚ÄîTop Hard Rock Albums, Top Independent Albums, and Top Rock Albums. ‚ÄúDistance‚Äù soared as the first of two #1 Rock Radio Hits and earned a GRAMMY¬Æ Award nomination for ‚ÄúBest Rock Song.‚Äù Two years later, Mammoth II only saw him pick up the pace. It debuted in the Top 5 of the Billboard Top Album Sales Chart in addition to bringing him back to #1 on the Top Hard Rock Albums Chart. It incited widespread applause from Rolling Stone, Guitar World, GRAMMY.com, Classic Rock, American Songwriter, and KERRANG! The band canvased the globe with Metallica and Pantera and supported Foo Fighters in North America as well as filling houses on their own. They performed on ABC‚Äôs Jimmy Kimmel LIVE!, at MusiCares 2024 gala in honor of Jon Bon Jovi, and Wolf took the stage at the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame¬Æ Induction of Ozzy Osbourne. Now, Wolfgang pushes forward on Mammoth‚Äôs third full-length LP.

--
DYING TO LOVE // LYRICS

Driving home with nowhere to be
Passing ghosts that tire of sleep
Blurry faces staring at me
They‚Äôre staring but they don‚Äôt see a thing

I‚Äôve been dying to love, dying to love, dying to love
One more second‚Äôs enough, second to love, second to love

Stepping stones that bloody your feet
Sirens holding flowers of teeth
They call your name from ivory streets
But heaven isn‚Äôt quite what it seems

I‚Äôve been dying to love, dying to love, dying to love
One more second‚Äôs enough, second to love, second to love

They circle over the stain, my essence slipping away
Waiting their turn for a taste

So tell me how does it taste?
And was it all worth the wait? So was it worth what it takes?

snippet.title: I Went Gambling at a Shopping Mall Casino!
snippet.description:
We are BACK at the Casino, or‚Ä¶ are we? We are BACK at a Shopping Mall, and we‚Äôre Gambling BABY! Can we get a shopping mall hand-pay for the memories, I mean why not? Thank you all for watching! You‚Äôre all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I‚Äôll see you in the next one! Let‚Äôs go to war!

Play your favorite slots and table games completely for free at: https://spinquest.com/?u=brettski

Brettski strutted through the sliding glass doors of the **Neon Valley Mall**, camera in hand, his reflection flickering in every chrome surface. Today‚Äôs video wasn‚Äôt just another vlog‚Äîit was *‚ÄúTurning $100 into $10,000 at the Mall Casino.‚Äù* His subscribers loved the rush, the lights, the madness.

The casino sat deep inside the mall like a glittering heart, pulsing with noise and flashing colors. Brettski set up his camera near the roulette table, grinning. ‚ÄúAlright guys, you know the rule‚Äîdouble or nothing till we strike gold.‚Äù

The first few spins went his way. Black 17. Red 32. Cheers erupted from nearby players as Brettski‚Äôs stack of chips grew. ‚ÄúThis is it!‚Äù he said, winking at the lens. ‚ÄúWe‚Äôre breaking the algorithm and the odds!‚Äù

But luck, like fame, burns fast. The wheel turned cruel. Bets vanished. His $100 became $10, then $5. A pit boss with a tight smile leaned over. ‚ÄúMaybe time to cash out, YouTuber?‚Äù

Brettski wasn‚Äôt done. He slid his last chip onto black. The wheel spun. The ball danced‚Äîand landed on red. The crowd groaned. The dealer reached for the chip, but the lights above flickered, then died.

A hush fell over the casino. When the backup lights buzzed on, Brettski‚Äôs camera was still rolling‚Äîbut his stack of chips was gone. So was the dealer. So was the pit boss.

He turned slowly. The tables were empty. Slot machines stood silent. Even the air felt wrong. On the camera screen, the live feed still showed *him*‚Äîbut behind the digital Brettski, the casino was full of people cheering.

The video counter kept running.

Then his phone vibrated with a notification:
**‚ÄúLIVE: Brettski Wins $10,000 at Neon Valley Mall.‚Äù**

Except‚Ä¶ he wasn‚Äôt streaming.

snippet.title: Halo: Campaign Evolved Is a Pretty Remake Coming to PS5, but Not an Exact One
snippet.description:
We played an early-in-development chunk of the classic Silent Cartographer mission in Halo: Campaign Evolved, the upcoming Unreal Engine 5 remake of Halo: Combat Evolved that's due out in 2026 for Xbox, PC, and yes, PlayStation 5. It's not quite a 1:1 remake though, so IGN's veteran of every Halo battle, Ryan McCaffrey, is here to give you his first impressions and tell you about what's new and what's been changed.

#IGN #Gaming #Halo

snippet.title: Roblox Grow A Garden In A Nutshell
snippet.description:
Play War Thunder for FREE on PC, PS, and Xbox ‚Äî https://wtplay.link/tankfish 
üî•Use the link to get the exclusive decal and other bonuses! üî• 
üí•WT Mobile ‚Äî https://wtm.game/tankfishwtm

Roblox Grow A Garden is a farming simulator game where players buy rare seed packs, plant them, and grow crops to sell for the in-game currency, Sheckles. The main goal is to expand your garden, earn more money to purchase rarer and more expensive seeds, and collect all the rare plants, aka the Divine, Prismatic, and Transcendent plants.

The game also features pets, which you can hatch from pet eggs. Pets have unique abilities that help your garden, such as increasing crop size, giving crops mutations, or accelerating growth speeds. Like plants, pets come in different rarities : Divine, Prismatic, and Transcendent.
Grow A Garden has a stock system for seeds and pets. The items available are random, so even if you are the richest player in Grow A Garden, you still can‚Äôt get all the rare seeds if they‚Äôre not currently in stock.

Similar to Fisch, plants and pets in Grow A Garden can be mutated. Mutated plants sell for more money, and the type of mutation depends on the weather and the pets you have. The best mutations only occur in very rare weather conditions. Pets can also mutate, giving special modifiers that improve their abilities. 

You can buy tools to assist your garden, like the Grandmaster Sprinkler, which increases the chance of plant mutations and the likelihood of giant fruits. The tool shop also follows a stock system, so items aren‚Äôt always available.

I unfortunately missed the whole Admin abuse event, which meant losing out on free Prismatic and Transcendent seeds and pets, so sadge.

In this video, I‚Äôll be showing full Grow A Garden gameplay while sharing useful tips and a complete guide to progress from noob to pro quickly (just trade bro, ask a hardcore GROW A Garden player for free giveaway and money). You can also troll other players by stealing their fruits using Robux. There‚Äôs no real way to prevent it other than playing in a private server. Stealing someone‚Äôs most expensive and rare fruits for 40 robux is such a chaotic prank.

The game constantly receives updates and events, making it tricky to keep up, the new Fall Update added a variety of seasonal and Halloween-themed seeds and pets.

So yeah, just like the other Roblox In A Nutshell videos, I‚Äôll try to cover everything Grow A Garden has to offer: gameplay, seed packs, mutations, pets, plants, events, weathers, size and more. As always, this Roblox video is packed with jokes, memes, funny moments, montages, and cursed edits. If you enjoyed this video, hit the like and the subscribe button and comment E.

Also giant plants and pets are a myth bro, it‚Äôs all RNG.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This video contains a crap load of dead memes and bad jokes. Viewer discretion advised.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Be sure to leave a like if you enjoyed this Roblox video!
Thanks for watching!
Like and subscribe for more Roblox Grow A Garden and other funny videos.

Roblox- Grow A Garden: 

Are you ready to grow your very own garden? Buy seeds from the shop when they restock, plant them, wait for them to grow, and collect the profits! Flex fruits and finds on friends, and have fun!

What is ROBLOX? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet¬≠to¬≠be¬≠dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúROBUX‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Roblox Grow A Garden is a farming simulator game where players buy rare seed packs, plant them, and grow crops to sell for the in-game currency, Sheckles. The main goal is to expand your garden, earn more money to purchase rarer and more expensive seeds, and collect all the rare plants, aka the Divine, Prismatic, and Transcendent plants.

The game also features pets, which you can hatch from pet eggs. Pets have unique abilities that help your garden, such as increasing crop size, giving crops mutations, or accelerating growth speeds. Like plants, pets come in different rarities : Divine, Prismatic, and Transcendent.
Grow A Garden has a stock system for seeds and pets. The items available are random, so even if you are the richest player in Grow A Garden, you still can‚Äôt get all the rare seeds if they‚Äôre not currently in stock.

Similar to Fisch, plants and pets in Grow A Garden can be mutated. Mutated plants sell for more money, and the type of mutation depends on the weather and the pets you have. The best mutations only occur in very rare weather conditions. Pets can also mutate, giving special modifiers that improve their abilities. 

You can buy tools to assist your garden, like the Grandmaster Sprinkler, which increases the chance of plant mutations and the likelihood of giant fruits. The tool shop also follows a stock system, so items aren‚Äôt always available.

I unfortunately missed the whole Admin abuse event, which meant losing out on free Prismatic and Transcendent seeds and pets, so sadge.

In this video, I‚Äôll be showing full Grow A Garden gameplay while sharing useful tips and a complete guide to progress from noob to pro quickly (just trade bro, ask a hardcore GROW A Garden player for free giveaway and money). You can also troll other players by stealing their fruits using Robux. There‚Äôs no real way to prevent it other than playing in a private server. Stealing someone‚Äôs most expensive and rare fruits for 40 robux is such a chaotic prank.

The game constantly receives updates and events, making it tricky to keep up, the new Fall Update added a variety of seasonal and Halloween-themed seeds and pets.

So yeah, just like the other Roblox In A Nutshell videos, I‚Äôll try to cover everything Grow A Garden has to offer: gameplay, seed packs, mutations, pets, plants, events, weathers, size and more. As always, this Roblox video is packed with jokes, memes, funny moments, montages, and cursed edits. If you enjoyed this video, hit the like and the subscribe button and comment E.

Also giant plants and pets are a myth bro, it‚Äôs all RNG.

snippet.description:
The rare German Tiger II 10.5cm used to be an extremely powerful tank in War Thunder, but some WT players aren't so sure anymore. It recently had its APHE round nerfed so that it doesn't overpressure, but it does have a lot more penetration. So is it really a nerf or a buff?
